Package: idionet
Type: Package
Title: Idiographic Network Estimation from Intensive Longitudinal Data
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person("Mohammed", "Saqr", role = c("aut", "cre"),
    email = "mohammed.saqr@uef.fi")
Description: Person-specific and within-person network estimation from
    intensive longitudinal and panel data. Provides graphical vector
    autoregression (graphical VAR), multilevel vector autoregression
    (mlVAR), and Group Iterative Multiple Model Estimation (GIMME) as
    clean-room implementations. Split out of the 'Nestimate' package so the
    idiographic time-series methods carry their own dependencies. Results are
    'cograph_network' objects rendered by 'cograph::splot()'.
License: GPL-3
Encoding: UTF-8
